column5: Yep, Talladega Baby!!!  Gonna be a great race.  Have fun with the Redneck's G.  See, you started the nudity thing, now look whatcha gone and done, half nekked beer belly boys!!!  (probably hairy too   ).  Joey
The hosers 'round here line up at the liquor store at 10am eh?
Talladega is always fun it`s one of the few Nascar races worth watching nowadays.
I'll pass on fishing Sunday so I can watch the race and wait for the "big one". Yep I gotta be crazy to put Nascar before fishing.
Great post G, gave me a good chuckle! I'm thinking the only safe place on Talladega Race Weekend is the public library. -Brian
It's supposed to rain there on Sunday GCD, so the crowds might be in town for a day or two longer that you anticipate. Dang NASCAR fans anyways...
I'm going to be off the lake just in time to catch the second half of the race.  How close to Talladega do you live??
i get dizzy just thinkin about nascar round and round and round woo hoo, not.
Yer gonna be up to yer trailer skirts in renex untill those boys race in circles.Better hope it doesn't get postponed. Joe
wow...thats pretty close.  I'm watching the Nationwide race right now.
Thanks for the live update GCD!!
Go Kenny Schrader!    Starting 3rd spot today.
Too bad about Kenny.One of the best all time guys to race.His book is very good and gives some insight into racing. Joe
